author: veithen
msg: Prevent the unit tests in the jaxws module from creating a log file in the project's base directory, because this file will never be cleaned and because it ends up in the source distribution. Note that this change was done in r817877 on the trunk.

author: davsclaus
msg: CAMEL-3031: Camel fails to start if an existing CamelContext has been registered in MBeanServer. Introduced pluggable strategy to auto assign camel context name.
